RPS's Scripts Package
=====================

rps-help@cs.northwestern.edu

Scripts implements various scripts that are used to glue RPS
prediction components together and to manage the complexity of the RPS
system.


Host load measurement
---------------------

start_hostloadmeasure.pl
 - start host load measurement on this host

start_hostloadmeasure_on.pl
 - start host load measurement on a specific host

start_hostloadmeasure_list.pl
 - start host load measurement on a list of hosts

kill_hostloadmeasure.pl
 - stop host load measurement on this host

kill_hostloadmeasure_on.pl
 - stop host load measurement on specific host

kill_hostloadmeasure_list.pl
 - stop host load measurement on a list of hosts


