General utilities
-----------------

clean_loadserver.pl
 - Run loadserver with cleaned up output - two numbers per line

clean_vmstat.pl
 - Run vmstat with cleaned up output - three numbers per line

kill_matching.pl
 - kill matching processes

select_from_loadtrace.pl
 - grab a portion of a load trace